@page "/services"
@layout MainLayout

<PageTitle>Services | SPC Technology</PageTitle>

<section class="section">
    <div class="container">
        <p class="eyebrow">Services</p>
        <h1>Implementation and Services</h1>
        <p class="lead">
            SPC Technology provides the professional services required to successfully implement, adapt, and operate Phoebus ERP in real business environments.
        </p>
        <p>
            Our services cover the full lifecycle of ERP adoption from initial implementation and data migration to system integration,
            training, and long-term operational support.
        </p>
        <p>
            Each engagement is designed around practical business requirements, ensuring that Phoebus ERP aligns with real operational workflows
            rather than forcing businesses to adapt to rigid software structures.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--alt">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-shell">
            <div class="section-header">
                <h2 class="section-title">Implementation and Deployment</h2>
                <p class="section-intro">
                    Successful ERP projects require careful planning, structured configuration, and reliable rollout support.
                </p>
            </div>
            <p>
                SPC Technology works closely with customers to prepare the system environment, configure the platform according to operational
                requirements, and guide the organization through the transition to a unified ERP system.
            </p>
            <p>Implementation services include:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Implementation planning and project preparation</li>
                <li>System configuration aligned with business processes</li>
                <li>Workflow design and operational alignment</li>
                <li>Controlled rollout and go-live support</li>
                <li>Post-deployment stabilization</li>
            </ul>
            <p>
                Our approach focuses on practical ERP adoption, ensuring that the system supports daily operations from the first day of use.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-shell">
            <div class="section-header">
                <h2 class="section-title">Customization and Business Adaptation</h2>
                <p class="section-intro">
                    Every business operates with unique processes, reporting requirements, and operational structures.
                </p>
            </div>
            <p>
                Phoebus ERP is designed to be flexible and adaptable, allowing the platform to evolve alongside business needs.
            </p>
            <p>Customization services include:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Adapting workflows to match operational processes</li>
                <li>Extending system functionality where required</li>
                <li>Integrating business-specific reporting and data structures</li>
                <li>Supporting specialized operational requirements</li>
            </ul>
            <p>
                This flexibility allows organizations to benefit from a structured ERP system while maintaining the operational practices
                that make their business effective.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--alt">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-shell">
            <div class="section-header">
                <h2 class="section-title">Data Migration</h2>
                <p class="section-intro">
                    Transitioning from existing systems to a unified ERP platform requires careful preparation of business data.
                </p>
            </div>
            <p>
                SPC Technology assists organizations in migrating data from legacy systems, spreadsheets, or fragmented operational tools
                into Phoebus ERP.
            </p>
            <p>Migration services include:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Analysis and preparation of existing data sources</li>
                <li>Structured data transformation and validation</li>
                <li>Migration of financial, operational, and inventory records</li>
                <li>Verification and reconciliation after migration</li>
            </ul>
            <p>
                This ensures that the new ERP environment starts with reliable and consistent data.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-shell">
            <div class="section-header">
                <h2 class="section-title">Training and Operational Support</h2>
                <p class="section-intro">
                    Successful ERP adoption depends on user confidence and operational understanding.
                </p>
            </div>
            <p>
                SPC Technology provides structured training and support services to help teams adopt Phoebus ERP effectively.
            </p>
            <p>Training and support services include:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>User training for finance and operational teams</li>
                <li>Administrator training for internal system management</li>
                <li>Onboarding assistance during early system usage</li>
                <li>Ongoing support for operational issues and system questions</li>
            </ul>
            <p>
                Our goal is to ensure that the ERP system becomes a productive tool rather than a technical barrier.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--alt">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-shell">
            <div class="section-header">
                <h2 class="section-title">Integration Services</h2>
                <p class="section-intro">
                    Many organizations rely on multiple software systems for different aspects of their operations.
                </p>
            </div>
            <p>
                SPC Technology provides integration services that allow Phoebus ERP to connect with other business systems where required.
            </p>
            <p>Integration services include:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Connecting ERP processes with external systems</li>
                <li>Integrating operational data flows</li>
                <li>Supporting API-based or system-level integration</li>
                <li>Enabling consistent data exchange between platforms</li>
            </ul>
            <p>
                This ensures that Phoebus ERP can operate as the central system within a broader business technology environment.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

