                </p>
            </div>
            <p>Services may include:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Server environment preparation</li>
                <li>System hosting or infrastructure support</li>
                <li>Operational monitoring assistance</li>
                <li>Technical consulting for ERP infrastructure</li>
            </ul>
            <p>
                These services help organizations maintain a stable and reliable environment for long-term ERP operations.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

